这里开始。” </p><blockquote class="tiktok-embed" cite="https://www.tiktok.com/@joe_haircut123/video/7362011726344129834" data-video-id="7362011726344129834" data-embed-from="oembed" style="max-width:605px; min-width:325px;"><section> <a target="_blank" title="@joe_haircut123" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@joe_haircut123?refer=embed">@joe_haircut123</a></p><p> <a title="活结" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/slipknot?refer=embed">#slipknot</a> <a title="活结扇" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/slipknotfans?refer=embed">#slipknotfans</a> <a title="帕皮和哈里茨" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/pappyandharriets?refer=embed">#pappyandharriets</a> <a title="先锋镇" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/pioneertown?refer=embed">#pioneertown</a></p><p> <a target="_blank" title="♬ 原声 - Joe_Haircut" href="https://www.tiktok.com/music/original-sound-7362011867562249006?refer=embed">♬ 原声 – Joe_Haircut</a> </section></blockquote><p><script async src="https://www.tiktok.com/embed.js"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="pt" dir="ltr">活结活结 (Slipknot) 的视频！！！！ <a href="https://t.co/zB79aAziHs">pic.twitter.com/zB79aAziHs</a></p><p> — 东元 (@Edukator_Teco) <a href="https://twitter.com/Edukator_Teco/status/1783699462038098388?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 4 月 26 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="und" dir="ltr"> 555666 <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/slipknot?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#slipknot</a> <a href="https://t.co/al2zMyBOeA">pic.twitter.com/al2zMyBOeA</a></p><p> - 维尼 (@vinitracky) <a href="https://twitter.com/vinitracky/status/1783706040929747346?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 4 月 26 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>打击乐手兼创始成员<a href="https://www.n